Class Char2ObjectAVLTreeMap<V>

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
Char2ObjectFunction<V>, Char2ObjectMap<V>, Char2ObjectSortedMap<V>, Function<Character,V>, Serializable, Cloneable, Function<Character,V>, IntFunction<V>, Map<Character,V>, SortedMap<Character,V>
public class Char2ObjectAVLTreeMap<V> extends AbstractChar2ObjectSortedMap<V> implements Serializable, Cloneable
A type-specific AVL tree map with a fast, small-footprint implementation.

The iterators provided by the views of this class are type-specific bidirectional iterators. Moreover, the iterator returned by iterator() can be safely cast to a type-specific list iterator.

      public Char2ObjectAVLTreeMap<V> clone()
      Returns a deep copy of this tree map.
